'''Cassandra Kelly''' is Addison's lawyer.

==History==
Cassandra was present as Addison's counsel during her final adoption hearing for Henry. When they learned that [[Mildred Clemons]] said she had concerns, which forced the judge to postpone the adoption, Cassandra asked Addison if anything unusual had happened at Mildred's last visit. Addison remembered that she'd met Jake and found out about his prior arrest. Addison was worried she could lose Henry.

==Career==
She is a lawyer.
